	 <content><p>本文作者：Sheldon</p>
<p><a href="http://cdn.songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/lianhechupin.png"><img src="http://cdn.songshuhui.net/wp-content/uploads/lianhechupin-600x293.png" alt="lianhechupin" width="600" height="293" class="alignleft size-large wp-image-96673" /></a></p>
