	 <title>异闻录 20：我们中出了个叛徒</title>
	 <link>/home/lbz/github/all/C++/SearchSource/data/rss源语料/phonekr.xml</link>
	 <content><div id="wmd-preview-section-30">
<p><a href="http://www.phonekr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/191.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-14194" alt="" src="http://www.phonekr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/191.jpg" width="640" height="428" /></a></p>
<blockquote><p>三星的律师翻来覆去说的全都是些无关紧要、有意误导甚至不实的指控，这些无疑已经让法官苹果公司造成了先入为主的影响。（Samsung’s counsel repeatedly made irrelevant, misleading, and even untrue statements that have undoubtedly caused the jury to form impressions that are highly prejudicial to Apple.）</p></blockquote>
<p style="text-align: right;">苹果律师专利诉讼庭上<a href="http://www.cnet.com/news/apple-samsung-made-prejudicial-and-false-statements-during-opening-argument/#ftag=CAD590a51e" target="_blank">直斥三星</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.phonekr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/62.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-14196" alt="" src="http://www.phonekr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/62.jpg" width="640" height="479" /></a></p>
<p>「权力游戏」让<a href="http://beautifuldeath.com/">死亡更加精彩</a></p>
