	 <title>极客公园环聊日常 —— 由 IUNI 引发的杂谈</title>
	 <link>/home/lbz/github/all/C++/SearchSource/data/rss源语料/phonekr.xml</link>
	 <content><blockquote><p>今天晚上龚叔 (+Carlos Gong) 在环聊里转发了一条 IUNI 的微博, 引发了一场挺有启发的讨论.</p></blockquote>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>出场人物:</p>
<p>+Geoffrey<span id="8cd4d8ef-b3f7-4d95-965a-a99360f17a51"><span class="GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark" id="e373b78e-f030-4968-8436-41e2eecc0307">.</span></span>R HSU: 我 (全程打酱油)</p>
<p>+王洪森: <a title="新浪微博" href="http://weibo.com/jason2be" target="_blank">@王洪森</a> (主角 1)</p>
<p>+Carlos Gong: <a title="新浪微博" href="http://weibo.com/carloslol" target="_blank">@冬虫夏草卡洛斯</a> (主角 2)</p>
<p>+John York: <a title="新浪微博" href="http://weibo.com/p/1005051430854652" target="_blank">@detecti1914</a> (吐槽役 1)</p>
<p>+Tony Qian: <a title="新浪微博" href="http://weibo.com/tonyq0802" target="_blank">@tonyq0802</a> (吐槽役 2)</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Part 1: IUNI 与动画</h3>
<p>Carlos Gong &#8211; 6:48 PM</p>
<blockquote><p><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fp%2F1006063840873722&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNEo1IlnfQXvmxgZZyY5V9k06eIIlg" target="_blank">http://weibo.com/p/<wbr></wbr>1006063840873722</a> 我得说，作为第一个版本，INUI 似乎没让人太失望。</p>
<p>PPT 整体上比老罗/李楠/雷军都要舒服些。<wbr></wbr>虽然小细节上值得吐槽的地方有。</p></blockquote>
<p>王 洪森 &#8211; 6:52 PM</p>
